  "description": "During training, randomly zeroes some channels of the input tensor\nwith probabilitypfrom a Bernoulli distribution (For a 5-dimensional tensor with\na shape of\\(NCDHW\\), the channel feature map refers to a 3-dimensional feature\nmap with a shape of\\(DHW\\)).",
